  move media-tv to virtual/linuxtv-dvb-headers, bug #403929

  14 May 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  files/libdvb-0.5.5.1-autotools.patch:
  fix autotools patch to use AC_PROG_CXX so that it works with libtool 2.2
  too

  04 May 2008; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  +files/libdvb-0.5.5.1-gcc43.patch, libdvb-0.5.5.1-r3.ebuild:
